{"type": "article", "id": 15017, "title": "Bra当上衣，廓形夹克和同色系套装｜每天都有流行关键词", "description": "我们每天为你总结秀场流行元素。", "date": "2015-09-17T08:31:51Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 7048, "name": "纽约时装周"}, {"id": 4625, "name": "Bra"}, {"id": 341, "name": "运动"}, {"id": 1782, "name": "Coach"}], "category": 19, "author": 113313, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 30, "image": "img/article/article_show/201607021247074zEMDFuLy1NKGT7k.png", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t纽约时间 9 月 15 日的秀场上，又有很多品牌再次出现了“露肩”、“低腰裤”、“竖条纹”等等元素，这在<span>我们上一篇总结的“流行关键词”中都有提到。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702124702gTpaNfdhZzYtiWOK.jpg\" width=\"858\" height=\"647\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.75407925\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\tMilly，竖条纹与露肩\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702124702tfuU1BwjRoGcvlW9.jpg\" width=\"858\" height=\"647\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.75407925\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\tVera Wang／Diesel Black Gold\r\n</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t<span>除此之外又出现了哪些值得注意的设计元素呢？结合之前几天的重量级品牌一起看今天的盘点：</span> \r\n</div>\r\n<h4>\r\n\tBra 当上衣 ：\r\n</h4>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t可以说是抹胸，有的更接近运动 Bra，这和运动风的兴起有很大关系，运动 girl 和时尚博主早已这样穿搭拍了 N 条街。从短的露腰上衣，到只穿运动 Bra，更全方位展示你蓄谋已久的马甲线。健康的性感，下面搭裙子，外面穿外套都挺方便。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702124703g3slUESCMfxn9uha.jpg\" width=\"858\" height=\"647\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.75407925\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<em>Vera Wang </em> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702124703a5iwmK4yZIg1vjfl.jpg\" width=\"858\" height=\"647\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.75407925\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<em>Rebecca Minkoff／</em><span><em>Alexander Wang</em></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702124704Da89WO7F1P4ximcK.jpg\" width=\"858\" height=\"647\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.75407925\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\tThakoon／Dennis Basso\r\n</p>\r\n<h4>\r\n\t廓形夹克：\r\n</h4>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t帅气注重线条的廓形夹克，是 cool girl 的最好选择，这几季大热的中性风最具代表性的单品之一。皮质、太空棉、网状……不同面料有不同感觉。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607021247043zYH2c8CTD46QNS5.jpg\" width=\"858\" height=\"647\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.75407925\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<em>Diesel Black Gold</em> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702124705lDiasuQ47KPwXFpo.jpg\" width=\"858\" height=\"647\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.75407925\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<em>Rag &amp; Bone</em> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702124705Fq2ABwOf6MXWZG13.jpg\" width=\"858\" height=\"647\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.75407925\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<em>Vivienne Tam</em> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<h4>\r\n\t同色系套装：\r\n</h4>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t同花色和同种条纹的上下套装，搭配一脚蹬或是运动鞋、凉鞋，增添更多休闲感。既保留了原本修饰体型的功能，又冲淡了正装与生俱来的严肃、死板。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702124706cZkMoqPgJSRipnW8.jpg\" width=\"858\" height=\"647\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" style=\"text-align:center;\" data-ratio=\"0.75407925\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<em>Coach</em> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702124706sw2NrhETUSMl5pv6.jpg\" width=\"858\" height=\"647\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.75407925\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<em>Diesel Black Gold</em><em>／Rag &amp; Bone</em> \r\n</div>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702124707Wh8sdNViZH0Cngj7.jpg\" width=\"858\" height=\"647\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.75407925\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<em>Sophie Theallet／Givenchy </em> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\n\n"}